com.camerontec.util.logger.slf4j

Class Slf4jMDCAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.util.logger.slf4j.Slf4jMDCAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ILoggerContext

    public final class Slf4jMDCAdapter
extends Object
implements ILoggerContext
    An adapter between ILoggerContext and org.slf4j.MDC.

    This implementation delegates to the org.slf4j.MDC without any error checking.
